clear of clouds until 2300 local time when conditions will become overcast at 1,000 feet with 
tops at 3,000 feet, occasional visibility of 3 statute miles in mist.  The outlook is MVFR.  
Southern coastal waters were forecast as overcast 1,000 feet with tops between 3,000 and 
4,000, and visibility 3 statute miles in mist.  The outlook was IFR due to ceilings and mist.
